==============================ie supports==============
1. http://selectivizr.com/           
selectivizr is a JavaScript utility that emulates CSS3 pseudo-classes and attribute selectors in Internet Explorer 6-8.
2.  https://github.com/scottjehl/Respond
A fast & lightweight polyfill for min/max-width CSS3 Media Queries (for IE 6-8, and more)


============================other==================
1. https://github.com/alexrabarts/jquery-platformselector          
platformSelector is a simple jQuery plugin that adds classes to the body element representing the browser's environment
2.  https://github.com/realjoshharrison/jquery-disablescroll
Disables scroll events from mousewheels, touchmoves and keypresses.

